description: The stuff hit the fan this week as bloggers, reps, and manufacturers are ALL up in arms over last week's show. Hear what they have to say about what we had to say. Plus Fred Smith joins us to talk about the World Championships of Musical Chairs and how it relates to ...Ellen Degeneres?
